Cerry123:

:mad: i have downloaded the whole thing extracted it but yet still it will only let me onto the hybird thing!!! what shud i do??[br][size=1]Posted at: September 16, 2006, 04:42:30 PM[/size][hr] :mad: plz someone answer!!!

You have do File, New Server, then type in the server IP for the server. You can find a list of servers at http://moparisthebest.com/serverstatus.php/, but please post private-server related questions on http://moparisthebest.com/smf. You can use the same account as you’re using here, you just have to log in over there.
